parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the windshield wipers can cause obstructed visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially during rain or snow.
symptoms: Windshield wipers become inoperable
work intermittently
stop in the middle of the windshield
or require shaking of wires or knocking on the wiper motor to function temporarily.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vibration of the rearview exterior mirror can cause loss of visibility, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Rearview exterior mirror vibrates excessively.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can lead to a loss of control, extended stopping distances, and increased risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal pulsates when braking
there is a lack of braking power in emergency stops
the brakes fail to immediately respond when the brake pedal is depressed
the brakes lock up
and the brakes make noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause a loss of braking power, leading to extended stopping distances and increased risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes fail to respond immediately when the brake pedal is depressed
the brakes lock up
and the brakes make noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS sensor can cause the ABS system to malfunction, leading to a loss of control, extended stopping distances, and increased risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The ABS system fails to operate properly
and the brakes make noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vibration and noise can be a sign of a larger issue with the braking system, which can lead to a loss of control, extended stopping distances, and increased risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates and makes noise when slowing down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat frame can cause the seat to break or become unstable, which can lead to a loss of control while driving, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The seat frame is broken
the seat rocks back and forth while driving
parts of the seat have fallen off
the seat does not operate as it should
the seat rail is faulty.
